headline: HUM Misses Q2 Earnings on Higher Benefit Costs, Ups '25 EPS View
summary: Humana's Q2 earnings fall year over year on a declining membership base. Notably, 2025 adjusted EPS is currently forecasted at around $17.00, up from the earlier view of around $16.25.
